title: United Kingdom Imports Intra Eu - Miscellaneous Manufactured Articles
description: Imports Intra Eu - Miscellaneous Manufactured Articles in the United Kingdom decreased to 80.86 GBP Million in September from 91.27 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports Intra Eu - Miscellaneous Manufactured Arti in the United Kingdom averaged 46.32 GBP Million from 1996 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 117.35 GBP Million in March of 2020 and a record low of 4.60 GBP Million in February of 2015. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of Intra EU - Miscellaneous Manufactured.
author: Hm Customs And Excise
